    (6-gate fail-fast pipeline: data_quality → kill_switch → duplicate_filter →
    risk_gate → position_sizing → var_impact; constructor takes 6 injected deps +
    3 config params: var_threshold, quality_threshold, cooldown_seconds;
    _check_data_quality: get_latest_score, composite_score >= threshold;
    _check_kill_switch: is_halted with fail-safe on unavailability;
    _check_duplicate: find_signals by strategy/symbol/since, match direction+bar_timestamp;
    _check_risk_gate: proxy OrderRequest → check_order delegation;
    _compute_position_size: SizingRequest → compute_size, zero-size rejection;
    _check_var_impact: compute_var, |var_95| <= threshold;
    _build_rejected: helper for rejected evaluation persistence;
    structured logging with structlog at info/warning levels)
