### Track: Advanced Backtesting

M9 — Event-Driven Backtesting Engine
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-13
Verification:
  - libs/contracts/backtest.py: Extended BacktestResult with signal_summary field;
    added EquityCurvePoint, DrawdownPoint, SignalAttribution, BacktestSignalSummary
    (Phase 8 M9 signal-attribution extensions)
  - libs/contracts/interfaces/backtest_engine.py: BacktestEngineInterface ABC
    (run method: BacktestConfig → BacktestResult)
  - services/worker/research/backtest_engine.py: BacktestEngine
    (event-driven replay: fetch candles → sort chronologically →
    per-bar pipeline: update market price → process pending orders →
    candle buffer → compute_batch indicators → strategy.evaluate →
    signal attribution → submit order to PaperBrokerAdapter →
    equity curve + drawdown tracking; position sizing: 95% cash fraction;
    slippage: deducted from broker cash post-fill;
    metrics: total return, annualized return, max drawdown, Sharpe ratio,
    win rate, profit factor from round-trip trade pairing;
    structured logging with correlation_id)
  - tests/unit/test_backtest_engine.py: 34 tests
    (TestKnownOutcome 4: rising/declining/flat/round-trip,
    TestSignalAttribution 4: records created/fields/counts/empty,
    TestFillSimulation 3: next-bar-open fill/timestamps/qty match,
    TestCostModeling 4: commission reduces equity/slippage reduces equity/
    commission recorded/slippage recorded,
    TestEquityCurveAndDrawdown 6: populated/starts-at-initial/ends-at-final/
    drawdown populated/non-positive/max-drawdown-declining,
    TestPerformanceMetrics 6: positive return/zero return/win rate/
    profit factor/bars count/sharpe,
    TestMultiSymbol 2: all symbols processed/trades per symbol,
    TestIndicatorIntegration 1: indicator names populated,
    TestEdgeCases 4: single bar/empty data/config preserved/utc timestamp)
  - Total: 34 M9 tests passing, ruff clean

